{"tid":2487180,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"東週刊：揭香港Apple縮骨炒100人","createTime":"2021-04-13T11:20:04.000Z","updateTime":"2021-04-14T00:56:12.000Z","uid":260806,"like":38,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":56,"replies":[{"pid":"68b5def9f4cc0623765a20a04508c78b1478a378","tid":2487180,"uid":260806,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-04-13T11:20:04.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://ipfs.infura.io/ipfs/QmdPe8S6FYURwc4RcvCVcdqjSjF7VTi5wzA3NXVZPkReHL?filename=jj2CNOR.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fjj2CNOR.jpg&h=1e1b8519&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n&hellip;&hellip;<br />\n<br />\n有被炒員工向本刊申訴，指公司炒人手法非常「縮骨」，以員工早年享用公司福利參加體檢後，接受體檢公司贈品爲由，突然指該等行爲不恰當，拒絕作出任何賠償。<br />\n<br />\n大律師丁煌表示，即使公司向員工提供醫療福利，但真正參與體檢服務的是員工，所以體檢中心向客戶送贈的禮品與公司無關，「體檢中心是立約者，客人是受約者，贈品是一個服務承諾，基於這個大前提，提供醫療福利的公司，在這個合約上無任何角色，員工有權拿取贈品。」<br />\n<br />\n《東週刊》第 920 期 Book A 第 16 至 18 頁 新聞內幕<br />\n<a href=\"https://eastweek.my-magazine.me/main/toc/920\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Feastweek.my-magazine.me%2Fmain%2Ftoc%2F920&d=anIIoOx73pQIzJB4hJH11AZxBlA1GgcQN30t83kccHY%3D&h=038d46d2\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://eastweek.my-magazine.me/main/toc/920</a>"},{"pid":"ef51051e778a5ec434066cf4cc351a85307aae66","tid":2487180,"uid":2054,"like":36,"dislike":2,"score":34,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2021-04-13T11:21:17.000Z","msg":"東週都就執啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"361fb4a8013250c7bc7ce938cb8088163e7edcc6","tid":2487180,"uid":260806,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-13T11:23:29.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6fc4e1efc243ecea64247e3564482a67dfa548df","tid":2487180,"uid":198583,"like":2,"dislike":8,"score":-6,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-04-13T11:23:37.000Z","msg":"戇鳩<br />\n<br />\n唔撚炒都俾AI取代啦<br />\n<br />\n廢post<br />\n<br />\n拉"},{"pid":"eeecfd3d1fae4bf3cdabbf860f221da5431357fb","tid":2487180,"uid":61105,"like":18,"dislike":5,"score":13,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-13T11:23:46.000Z","msg":"以為講蘋果日報<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e45e399738f7ecfea6db066fcb43f91cd0eb855e","tid":2487180,"uid":241504,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-04-13T11:24:02.000Z","msg":"爆買282<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"92678ba871098c5106bedf04d88bd3de32df4ee6","tid":2487180,"uid":11148,"like":6,"dislike":8,"score":-2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-04-13T11:26:03.000Z","msg":"炒人咪炒人大把公司日日炒人仲閪過aapl,咁到攞黎講<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4d80f499639f90a68da7f1dca089e30b50d9fa7e","tid":2487180,"uid":10101,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-04-13T11:28:44.000Z","msg":"8名蘋果亞洲有限公司前員工入稟勞資審裁處，向該公司追討遣散費或長期服務金、代通知金、假期補償以及公司股份，惟蘋果亞洲有限公司反指8名前員工涉及詐騙行為，案件今日(1日)於勞資審裁處第一次聆訊，由於須裁斷欺詐行為是否屬實，被告人需於明年1月26日，將簽名供詞以掛號形式，寄予法庭及各申訴人；而各申訴人亦須於明年3月26日，就被告人供詞作書面答覆，案件押後至明年5月24日再審議。<br />\n案情指，8名蘋果亞洲有限公司前員工於2018年使用公司福利，參加健身課程後收取贈品，今年年初突被指涉及欺詐行為，要求停職調查，今年4月遭僱主以《僱傭條例》第9條解僱。<br />\n審裁官潘弘翰詢問被告人公司有否就事件報警處理，僱主代表答辯指未有報案，但已就事件作出調查及完成報告。審裁官提醒8名申索人，由於被告人以虛假單據作詐騙行為指控各申訴人，若法庭裁決後欺詐行為屬實，將會轉交警方或律政司作刑事調查，又詢問各申訴人會否先考慮律師意見後再作申訴決定，經休庭商議後，各申訴人維持提告決定。<br />\n工聯會權益委員副主任、勞顧會勞方代表鄧家彪於庭外透露，就他所知有近100名員工有類近情況，質疑蘋果公司因疫情下業績不佳而舊事重提。他續指，2018年發生的事件今年才追究，時間上的巧合難免令人聯想資方是因業績問題想炒人。"},{"pid":"e6770c47f6e76bf573e0a9482d0555e076047f42","tid":2487180,"uid":260806,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-13T11:28:59.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/cow/grab.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/cow/grab.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/cow/grab.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n炒幾多都唔識得反抗<br />\n無論幾過分嘅藉口<br />\n都係繼續炒人"},{"pid":"1712281db008eedff84a44c1d9a83ceae9a6a844","tid":2487180,"uid":313546,"like":22,"dislike":0,"score":22,"quote":{"pid":"92678ba871098c5106bedf04d88bd3de32df4ee6","tid":2487180,"uid":11148,"like":6,"dislike":8,"score":-2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-04-13T11:26:03.000Z","msg":"炒人咪炒人大把公司日日炒人仲閪過aapl,咁到攞黎講<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2021-04-13T11:29:58.000Z","msg":"appl賺緊錢 仲係全球top10(我估啦)賺錢嘅公司 咁都唔講咁都無咩可以講"},{"pid":"7fdff1381190aaf62e7a309ba2ae0e6aa33aba4e","tid":2487180,"uid":196968,"like":0,"dislike":2,"score":-2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-04-13T11:30:51.000Z","msg":"丁蝗<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"23ee1491b92497cff63d9fb37cedef1a8a04b43d","tid":2487180,"uid":245027,"like":14,"dislike":6,"score":8,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-13T11:32:13.000Z","msg":"炒撚晒佢啦<br />\n班apple狗又煩又串<br />\n拎得兩萬幾人工以為自己高人一等"},{"pid":"036acb27b9bcbabf883ea9085850a7c5a35241dc","tid":2487180,"uid":260806,"like":16,"dislike":0,"score":16,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-13T11:36:05.000Z","msg":"係法律問題：<br />\n<br />\n僱主應該留意，即時解僱是嚴重的紀律處分，只有在僱員犯了非常嚴重的過失或經多次警告仍不改善的情況下才採用。"},{"pid":"5437c4b464143ab4285d6c6a8a99eb6eedf964ba","tid":2487180,"uid":8410,"like":7,"dislike":1,"score":6,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-04-13T11:39:16.000Z","msg":"共果賺香港人咁多錢， 連賠足都唔肯咁仆街<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1e34b3222d39a2f0be3f2373aeb35b91a6225b34","tid":2487180,"uid":118805,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-13T11:39:49.000Z","msg":"嘩！<br />\n咁L無良！"},{"pid":"fec1a0ee6bc4e0777f99f38977a1989e9c56f7e4","tid":2487180,"uid":60635,"like":5,"dislike":4,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-13T11:40:15.000Z","msg":"美國佬一向炒人唔手軟，同佢打成一世工就笨<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7fd